  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Baggy Duo</strong> invites you to dive into a whimsical world of adventure and challenge as you embark on thrilling dungeon missions under the guidance of a mischievous Fairy. Explore beautifully crafted levels filled with secrets, puzzles, and enemies waiting to be defeated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Baggy Duo, you’ll encounter a variety of environments, each brimming with unique obstacles and treasures. Master the art of platforming as you navigate perilous traps and clever puzzles, all while uncovering the enchanting lore of the dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your adventure style with coop gameplay modes! Play solo to hone your skills and conquer each mission at your own pace, or grab a friend for local multiplayer mayhem. Team up to tackle challenges together, combining your abilities for an exhilarating co-op experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're a seasoned platforming veteran or a newcomer looking for fun, Baggy Duo offers engaging gameplay that will keep you on your toes. Are you ready to answer the Fairy’s call and uncover the mysteries that lie beneath the surface? Your adventure awaits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Mode</strong> : Enjoy sharpening your skills. to pass many obstacles and puzzles in this mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/e1da0a9296fbf3173fa75f236a953bc4.poster.avif?t=1754899239\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/e1da0a9296fbf3173fa75f236a953bc4.webm?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/e1da0a9296fbf3173fa75f236a953bc4.mp4?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coop-Gameplay</strong> : Enjoy more gameplay, overcome obstacles and puzzles with your trusted companion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/776ce9b10fc46426b500fb7c9d23159f.poster.avif?t=1754899239\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/776ce9b10fc46426b500fb7c9d23159f.webm?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/776ce9b10fc46426b500fb7c9d23159f.mp4?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ending Scene</strong> : Challenge your ability to collect all the items in the level to unlock the correct ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/ec8182e517c10aa838958ac6296c8c9d.avif?t=1754899239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras_big/ec8182e517c10aa838958ac6296c8c9d.avif?t=1754899239 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Characters</strong> : Unlock these adorable in-game characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/2f45d75962bd66ac83393b8d12428fc7.poster.avif?t=1754899239\" width=350 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/2f45d75962bd66ac83393b8d12428fc7.webm?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/2f45d75962bd66ac83393b8d12428fc7.mp4?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Baggy Duo</strong> invites you to dive into a whimsical world of adventure and challenge as you embark on thrilling dungeon missions under the guidance of a mischievous Fairy. Explore beautifully crafted levels filled with secrets, puzzles, and enemies waiting to be defeated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Baggy Duo, you’ll encounter a variety of environments, each brimming with unique obstacles and treasures. Master the art of platforming as you navigate perilous traps and clever puzzles, all while uncovering the enchanting lore of the dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your adventure style with coop gameplay modes! Play solo to hone your skills and conquer each mission at your own pace, or grab a friend for local multiplayer mayhem. Team up to tackle challenges together, combining your abilities for an exhilarating co-op experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're a seasoned platforming veteran or a newcomer looking for fun, Baggy Duo offers engaging gameplay that will keep you on your toes. Are you ready to answer the Fairy’s call and uncover the mysteries that lie beneath the surface? Your adventure awaits!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single Mode</strong> : Enjoy sharpening your skills. to pass many obstacles and puzzles in this mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/e1da0a9296fbf3173fa75f236a953bc4.poster.avif?t=1754899239\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/e1da0a9296fbf3173fa75f236a953bc4.webm?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/e1da0a9296fbf3173fa75f236a953bc4.mp4?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Coop-Gameplay</strong> : Enjoy more gameplay, overcome obstacles and puzzles with your trusted companion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/776ce9b10fc46426b500fb7c9d23159f.poster.avif?t=1754899239\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/776ce9b10fc46426b500fb7c9d23159f.webm?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/776ce9b10fc46426b500fb7c9d23159f.mp4?t=1754899239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ending Scene</strong> : Challenge your ability to collect all the items in the level to unlock the correct ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/ec8182e517c10aa838958ac6296c8c9d.avif?t=1754899239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras_big/ec8182e517c10aa838958ac6296c8c9d.avif?t=1754899239 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Characters</strong> : Unlock these adorable in-game characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282450/extras/2f45d75962bd66ac83393b8d12428fc7.poster.avif?t=1754899239\" width=350 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/ste